# NethWorksNet – Personal Website

## What It Is

A single-page personal "whois" landing site. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS, no framework or build step. Uses ES modules.

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `index.html` | Shell: header, nav, main content area |
| `javascript/app.js` | SPA logic: tab content, content injection, nav animation |
| `css/styles.css` | All styles |

## Tabs / Content Map

- **whois** (`data-tab="about"`): social profile links (YouTube, GitHub, LinkedIn), shown by default

## Dependencies

- None (no build step, no runtime dependencies)

## Design Tokens

- Background: `#201c29`
- Accent: `#ab49de`, `#d39fee`
- Font: Montserrat (Google Fonts)
